[SN]TITLE[SN]
Child sex abuser Henry Clarke tracked down to Canada

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
BBC News NI tracks down self-confessed paedophile Henry Clarke in Canada.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
5 April 2017 Last updated at 10:25 BST
Clarke admitted abusing boys in Northern Ireland in the 1960s and 1970s but was never brought to justice.
You can find out more about this story across BBC News NI on Wednesday.
